                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7857" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TEC-0117</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2959 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">顺“双碳”之势，走低碳之路——D海洋石油公司低碳技术创新探索</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Follow the “Dual Carbon” trend, take the low-carbon road—D offshore oil company low-carbon technological innovation exploration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李玥，白浪，解百臣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中海石油（中国）有限公司天津分公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石油工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海洋石油；技术创新；低碳转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">offshore oil ; innovation exploration; low-carbon transition</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">应对气候变化、控制温室气体已成为全球共识，2020年我国提出了“碳达峰碳中和”的目标，越来越多的企业顺应“双碳”大趋势，抓住历史机遇，围绕双碳目标开展低碳转型，不断提高企业核心竞争力，实现自身可持续发展。本案例以D海洋石油公司为例，描述了在“双碳”背景下，通过技术创新，最终在保障国家能源安全和油田绿色开发之间走出了一条具有海洋石油特色的低碳之路。通过本案例的分析与学习，引导学生掌握技术创新的内涵与实质、了解企业低碳技术创新的动力、阻碍因素以及实现途径，进一步加深学生对技术创新的认识，同时为其他企业在“双碳”目标下实现低碳转型提供学习的方向。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Tackling climate change and controlling greenhouse gases have become a global consensus.  In 2020, our country put forward the goal of “Peak carbon and carbon neutrality”. More and more enterprises adapt to the“Dual Carbon” trend, seize historical opportunities, carry out low-carbon transformation to achieve the dual-carbon goal, and constantly improve the core competitiveness of enterprises to achieve their own sustainable development. This case, taking D offshore oil company as an example, describes the process of technological innovation under the background of “Dual Carbon” target, finally, a road to reduce carbon emission with marine oil characteristics was found between the national energy security and the green development of  its oil fields. Through the analysis and study of this case, guide students to master the connotation and essence of technology innovation，understand the motive force，the hindrance factors of low-carbon innovation and the way to achieve it. Further, it can deepen students&#39; understanding of technological innovation, and provide learning direction for other enterprises to achieve low-carbon transformation under the“Dual Carbon” target.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新方法》、《技术创新与管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技术创新的概念；技术创新的激励与阻力、技术创新过程；技术创新的作用和效果</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
